---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
A plain © sign decodes in running text.

Monospace & decodes, as do a _(©) subscript, a ^(®) superscript, and a
~~©~~ deletion.

A link label &copy; keeps the entity literal, and so does a &copy; span
and a verbatim block:

    &copy;
